        <item>
            <title>乘客坐九巴大声播片屡劝不改，司机一句秒杀令他收声</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/21/bus-playing-video-with-loud-sound/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bus-playing-video-with-loud-sound</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/21/bus-playing-video-with-loud-sound/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 06:55:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[巴士]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293267</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前有乘客在车厢内大声聊天，九巴司机无法忍受下停车开咪怒骂乘客足足一分钟才能让乘客收声（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/kmb-tun-mun/fun-tech/">相关报道</a>），想不到「人类总要重复同样的错误」，日前又发生类似事件。网上流传一段九巴司机开咪高峰责骂乘客的影片。影片中显示一名乘客似乎在车厢内大声聊天，面对乘客无视其多次提醒，司机最终选择停车并使用车内咪高峰，发出近一分钟的怒骂，成功让那些喧哗的乘客收声，车厢也迅速回复平静。</p><p>网上有影片流传，显示 2 月 11 日一名九巴 P968 乘客在车厢内公然大声播放影片，严重影响其他乘客。司机见状广播劝阻，多次劝阻无效司机终于忍无可忍，果断开咪喝斥要求乘客停止播片，继续播放就会报警并拒绝开车。</p><p>影片源自 Facebook 群组「<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz x1sur9pj xkrqix3 xzsf02u x1s688f" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/646949689010059/?__cft__[0]=AZXGvVemyYCZMA2HC7YHLKqDCN72k8qD10En972FJIVbrr6pW4osVJnZep9LdOj_TgRIXgVHqK2Tpy-OGaKMtbFzqc20a_d1Ued9mbTSRsblYH5hIXjYE7nVXx7PzHlQ5jFPOscC_sT5GXT3K-oFgrZnPzKJu4HvXpEPfIzG_WuW-K1wv0BCLhltkE0we8oe41k&amp;__tn__=-UC%2CP-R"><span class="html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs">香港突发事故报料区及讨论区</span></a>」，事发时一名乘客用手机外放影片，音量极大，刺耳声响影响车厢安宁，司机透过广播多次提醒保持车厢安静」和「调低手提电脑音量」，惟对方依旧充耳不闻，态度顽固。见对方屡劝不改，司机最终决定开咪斥责，要求乘客停止播片，继续播放就会停车兼报警，他就可以「慢慢赚补水」。上传影片的网民引述乘客回应指：「使唔使咁串」，司机就表示：「点解咁串系因为按法例报警处理，多谢你畀到支持我」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293277" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120441-493x580.jpg" alt="" width="493" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120441-493x580.jpg 493w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120441.jpg 632w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 493px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz x1sur9pj xkrqix3 xzsf02u x1s688f" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/646949689010059/?__cft__[0]=AZXGvVemyYCZMA2HC7YHLKqDCN72k8qD10En972FJIVbrr6pW4osVJnZep9LdOj_TgRIXgVHqK2Tpy-OGaKMtbFzqc20a_d1Ued9mbTSRsblYH5hIXjYE7nVXx7PzHlQ5jFPOscC_sT5GXT3K-oFgrZnPzKJu4HvXpEPfIzG_WuW-K1wv0BCLhltkE0we8oe41k&amp;__tn__=-UC%2CP-R"><span class="html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs">香港突发事故报料区及讨论区</span></a></p><p>影片在网上广传后掀起讨论，网民力撑司机，认为他做法值得赞扬。有留言认为乘客应该自律，不要发出不必要噪音影响车长专注、骚扰其他乘客。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120207-694x82.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="82" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120207-694x82.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120207.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>有人为巴士司机抱打不平，直言：「应该平时忍够啲痴线佬成日播嘈（噪）音」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022115954-694x143.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="143" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022115954-694x143.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022115954.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>香港大学法律与科技研究中心指，根据《道路交通 (公共服务车辆) 规例》(第 374D 章) 第 46(1)(n)(i) 条，公共巴士之乘客或有意乘搭该等车辆的人，不得在车内或车上的时候使用或操作任何嘈吵的器具、乐器或任何留声机、收音机或录音机，而滋扰到任何其他人。任何人无合理辩解而违反第 46 条，即属犯罪，一经定罪，可处罚款 $3,000 及监禁 6 个月。</p><p>有兴趣观看司机如何反击的朋友可以点击下面连结：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/HKGuy/posts/2443225162715827/">https://www.facebook.com/groups/HKGuy/posts/2443225162715827/</a></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F813831777123798%2Fvideos%2F1152833099851264%2F%3Fidorvanity%3D1060857804356998&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=267&amp;t=0" width="267" height="476" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe><br />
图片来源：<a href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fd/V6P8_KMB_P968_18-07-2021%281%29.jpg">Wikipedia</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/HKGuy/posts/2443225162715827/">香港突发事故报料区及讨论区</a>、<a href="https://www.clic.org.hk/zh/topics/traffic_law/public_transport/public_bus/passenger_plays_loud_music">香港大学法律与科技研究中心</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
