        <item>
            <title>【实试】ASUS Prime RTX 5070 Ti O16G    挑战上代卡王 RTX 4090</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/20/asus-prime-rtx-5070-ti/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=asus-prime-rtx-5070-ti</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/20/asus-prime-rtx-5070-ti/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 20 Feb 2025 14:48:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293166</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今晚 RTX 5070 Ti 其他品牌评测都继续解禁，小编现到手的是 ASUS Prime RTX 5070 Ti O16G，即刻开箱试试佢啦。</p><p><a title="_DSC7289" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54339401701/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54339401701_43db92e4f9_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7289" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><h2>产品背景与市场定位</h2><p>今次到手评测的 5070 Ti 显卡，ASUS Prime RTX 5070 Ti O16G ，当然也是建基于 NVIDIA Blackwell 架构，专为游戏玩家和内容创作者设计，结合了高性能、小型化设计和先进的散热技术。RTX 5070 Ti 定位为中高阶显示卡，建议零售价（MSRP）为 HK$8,699。相比于 RTX 5080，性能差距约 11%-21%，但定价大约低 25% 左右 (当然以 NVIDIA 的正常价钱来说，不是炒价)，性价比是较为突出 (又说一次不是炒价)。与上一代 RTX 4070 Ti 和 4070 Ti Super 相比，性能有显著提升，市场定位为 1440p 重度游戏和轻度 4K 游戏，不过小编之后的测试都是以 4K 来测试的，特别是 Monster Hunter Wilds，4K 画面情况下看它够不够玩 。</p><p><a title="_DSC7293" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54339401686/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54339401686_05ebf6001f_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7293" width="1600" height="1067" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC7315" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54339401786/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54339401786_8918c1cd04_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7315" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><h2>SFF-Ready 的卡身设计</h2><p>ASUS Prime RTX 5070 Ti O16G 采用 2.5 槽设计，适合小型机箱（SFF-Ready），卡身尺寸为 304 x 126 x 50 mm（约 12 x 5 x 2 英寸），方便空间有限的用户使用。确保与小型机箱的相容性，特别适合需求机箱紧凑布局的玩家和创作者，卡上提供了三个 Display Port 及一个 HDMI 的输出接口。</p><p><a title="_DSC7302" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54338500062/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54338500062_32fb62dc03_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7302" width="1600" height="1067" /></a><br /><a title="_DSC7304" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54338500087/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54338500087_d76fababe2_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7304" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">三个 Display Port 及一个 HDMI</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC7296" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54339822860/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54339822860_b8be103c15_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7296" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><br /><b>
GPU Clock：2295 MHz<br />
Boost Clock：2497 MHz<br />
记忆体：16GB GDDR7<br />
记忆体速度：28 Gbps<br />
介面：1 x HDMI 2.1b, 3 x DisplayPort 2.1b<br />
尺寸：304 x 126 x 50 mm<br />
功耗：300W<br />
Slot：2.5 Slot</p><p>建议售价：HK$8,699</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293173" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gputweakiii20_2_2025-430x580.png" alt="" width="430" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gputweakiii20_2_2025-430x580.png 430w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gputweakiii20_2_2025.png 578w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 430px" /></p><h2>各方面实试</h2><p>小编就找来了上代的 RTX 4070 Ti，以及 RTX 4070，与今次的 ASUS Prime RTX 5070 Ti O16G 比较一下，各方面的能力，当然就先测试各位玩家最为关心的 Monster Hunter Wilds 啦。</p><p><a title="_DSC7360" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54339921520/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54339921520_c2bbffc98e_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7360" width="1600" height="1067" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><br /><b>
MB：ROG MAXIMUS Z890 EXTREME<br />
RAM：KLEVV CRAS V RGB ROG Certified D5-7200 32GB Kit<br />
SSD：Samsung 980 PRO PCle 4.0 NVMe M.2 1TB<br />
PSU：ROG Thor III 1200W<br />
Cooler：ROG RYUJIN III 360 ARGB EXTREME<br />
FAN：ASUS TUF Gaming TR120 ARGB Reverse FAN<br />
Case：ASUS TUF Gaming GT502 Horizon</p><p>(鸣谢 ASUS 提供测试平台)</p><p><a title="_DSC6989" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54292810550/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54292810550_87615c8da0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6989" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><h2>Monster Hunter Wilds</h2><h2><span style="color: #339966;">4K 画面 + 画格生成</span></h2><p>测试结果：小编先测试 4K 画面，画质设定为极高，Frame Gen On，光追 Off，在此极好画面设定下，RTX 5070 Ti 有 106 FPS，这个速度够玩 4K Mon Hunt Wilds 了。</p><p><a title="snap0145" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54339733823/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54339733823_e48f6ef429_h.jpg" alt="snap0145" width="1552" height="905" /></a></p><h2><span style="color: #339966;">4K 画面 + 光追 + 画格生成</span></h2><p>测试结果：之后就测试 4K 画面，画质设定为极高，Frame Gen On，光追今次都 On，RTX 5070 Ti 仍有 98 FPS，非常不错。</p><p><a title="snap0146" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54338612692/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54338612692_f8aa769050_h.jpg" alt="snap0146" width="1555" height="909" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
